Description: CLI tool for generating AI coding assistant rules
 AI Rules Generator is a powerful CLI tool that creates customized
 AI coding assistant rules based on your project configuration.
 .
 Features:
  - Interactive Setup: Configure once, use everywhere
  - Multi-Tool Support: Generates rules for 6 AI coding tools
  - Shared AI Rules: Creates .ai-rules/ directory
  - Multiple AI Providers: Support for OpenAI and Anthropic Claude
  - Monorepo Support: Automatically detects packages
  - Language & Framework Specific: 20+ languages, 100+ frameworks
  - Template Fallback: Works without AI API keys
